               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430612-name-748" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-748" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-748" type="surname" value="POLLARD"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-748" type="given" value="RICHARD"></interp>RICHARD POLLARD</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a grocer, and live in Union-street, Spitalfields. On the 13th of May I had a lump of sugar safe about seven minutes before I missed it—this is it—I know it because the paper is torn at the top—I swear to it—it weighs 41lbs. 2oz.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. PAYNE</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Did you ever weigh it? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes, before I lost it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430612-name-749" type="witnessName">
