                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-749" type="surname" value="DAVIES"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-749" type="given" value="WILLIAM DAY"></interp>WILLIAM DAY DAVIES</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable H</hi> 36.) I stopped the prisoner with this sugar, in Dorset-street, about a hundred yards from the prosecutor's—he threw it down, and ran about twenty yards—I ran after him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> Where did you stop him? A. In Fashion-street, the next street to where I saw him—I am quite sure I saw him throw it down—it was between eleven and twelve o'clock at night.</p>
